      "content": "The Graph decentralized network gateway accepts POST GraphQL queries against individual subgraphs. The query URL embeds the API key directly in the path; alternatively the API key may be supplied as an Authorization Bearer token. Each subgraph defines its own GraphQL schema.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: The Graph Docs",
